{
    "domain_model": "# Domain Kit for Dental Clinic Management System\n\n## Ubiquitous Language (Glossary)\n\n- **Patient**: An individual receiving dental care.\n- **Profile**: A collection of personal and medical information about a Patient.\n- **MedicalAlert**: A notification about a Patient's medical condition or allergy.\n- **Consent**: A record of a Patient's agreement to treatment.\n- **EHR (Electronic Health Record)**: A digital version of a Patient's paper chart.\n- **ClinicalNote**: A detailed note about a Patient's treatment or condition.\n- **Odontogram**: A graphical representation of a Patient's dental status.\n- **TreatmentLog**: A record of treatments provided to a Patient.\n- **Appointment**: A scheduled meeting between a Patient and a Dentist.\n- **Dentist**: A professional providing dental care.\n- **Invoice**: A bill for services rendered.\n- **PaymentPlan**: A structured payment schedule for an Invoice.\n- **InsuranceClaim**: A request for payment from an insurance company.\n- **Role**: A set of permissions assigned to a user (e.g., Receptionist, Dentist, Administrator).\n\n## Entities and Attributes\n\n- **Patient**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `String name`\n  - `LocalDate dateOfBirth`\n  - `List<MedicalAlert> medicalAlerts`\n  - `List<Consent> consents`\n  - `Profile profile`\n\n- **Profile**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `String address`\n  - `String phoneNumber`\n  - `String email`\n\n- **MedicalAlert**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `String description`\n  - `LocalDate dateIssued`\n\n- **Consent**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `String description`\n  - `LocalDate dateGiven`\n\n- **EHR**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `Patient patient`\n  - `List<ClinicalNote> clinicalNotes`\n  - `Odontogram odontogram`\n  - `List<TreatmentLog> treatmentLogs`\n\n- **ClinicalNote**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `String note`\n  - `LocalDate dateCreated`\n\n- **Odontogram**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `Map<String, String> toothStatus`\n\n- **TreatmentLog**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `String treatmentDescription`\n  - `LocalDate dateOfTreatment`\n\n- **Appointment**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `Patient patient`\n  - `Dentist dentist`\n  - `LocalDateTime scheduledTime`\n  - `AppointmentStatus status`\n\n- **Dentist**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `String name`\n  - `List<Appointment> appointments`\n\n- **Invoice**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `Patient patient`\n  - `BigDecimal amount`\n  - `List<PaymentPlan> paymentPlans`\n  - `List<InsuranceClaim> insuranceClaims`\n\n- **PaymentPlan**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `BigDecimal installmentAmount`\n  - `LocalDate dueDate`\n\n- **InsuranceClaim**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `String claimNumber`\n  - `BigDecimal claimAmount`\n  - `ClaimStatus status`\n\n- **Role**\n  - `UUID id`\n  - `String roleName`\n  - `List<User> users`\n\n## Relationships\n\n- **Patient** 1:N **MedicalAlert**\n- **Patient** 1:N **Consent**\n- **Patient** 1:1 **Profile**\n- **Patient** 1:1 **EHR**\n- **EHR** 1:N **ClinicalNote**\n- **EHR** 1:1 **Odontogram**\n- **EHR** 1:N **TreatmentLog**\n- **Patient** 1:N **Appointment**\n- **Dentist** 1:N **Appointment**\n- **Patient** 1:N **Invoice**\n- **Invoice** 1:N **PaymentPlan**\n- **Invoice** 1:N **InsuranceClaim**\n- **Role** 1:N **User**\n\n## Critical Business Rules and Invariants\n\n- A **Patient** must have a unique **Profile**.\n- An **Appointment** cannot be in the status of \"Completed\" if it has not been \"Confirmed\".\n- An **Invoice** must have a total amount equal to the sum of its **PaymentPlans**.\n- A **MedicalAlert** must be associated with a **Patient** and cannot exist independently.\n- A **Consent** must be recorded before any treatment is logged in the **TreatmentLog**.\n- **Role-based access control** must ensure that only users with the appropriate **Role** can access specific functionalities.",
